description:
Democrats want to take your guns. Whoopi Goldberg says AR-15s have to go, but you can keep your "yee haw guns." WH walks back Biden comments on handguns. Emotion over logic: CNN host claims panic attack dropping off kids at school. C&B take calls and Clay predicts the Johnny Depp-Amber Heard verdict.
